===Letter===
{{ARchar|'''ه '''/''' [[ﻫ]] '''/''' ‍ه‍ '''/''' ‍ه'''}} {{IPAchar|(hā’)}}

# The twenty-sixth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ن]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[و]]}}.
# The fifth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[د]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[و]]}}.

